column5: Is that an adipose fin, or a bit of ice/slush? If there is an adipose fin then I say rainbow smelt.
I fish ahmic lake and they have smelt in that lake.  I would second rainbow smelt.  Walleye get big feeding on them.
Looks like a smelt to me..does it stink? .bummer if it is
Does it have teeth? Looks like a smelt to me too.  S.
looks pretty small for a smelt
I posted the pic to refer to the same colour and lines.  Smelt  I know my pike bait. Right HH ? LOL
looks pretty small for a smelt All smelt will be that small at some point.  Even muskies and sturgeon start out smaller than that.
All smelt will be that small at some point.  Even muskies and sturgeon start out smaller than that.  TY
